Package: raveutils
Type: Package
Title: Utility Toolbox for RAVE package
Version: 0.5
Language: en-US
Authors@R: c(
    person("Zhengjia", "Wang", email = "dipterix.wang@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Beauchamp lab", email = "beauchamplab@gmail.com", role = c("cph", "fnd"))
    )
Description: Includes multiple cross-platform read/write interfaces for
  RAVE project: R analysis and visualization of human intracranial 
  electroencephalography data. Provides hybrid tensor array classes that 
  stores 10 GB level big array on solid state drives and load
  on demand within seconds. Defines RAVE context that are massively 
  used through out RAVE core package. Re-writes functions from other
  packages with more stable behavior and backward compatibility.
BugReports: https://github.com/beauchamplab/rave/issues
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
